headline: Fulton County, Georgia, to Modernize Land Records Management with Tyler Technologies
summary: PLANO, Texas, September 04, 2025--Tyler signed a contract with the Fulton County Clerk of Superior and Magistrate Courts’ office in GA for its Enterprise Records Management solution.
